
Ranger Help for: slots
======================

SYNTAX:      slots/slots #
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:    
Shows a Ranger how many slots he/she has available. It also shows which
skills are available to be learned by the Ranger. Slots are used to buy
skills with. Additional slots are gained as a Ranger's guild level
goes up. You may also type slots with a number between 1-15 as an argument
to see a list of skills in that slot level.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: glevels, myskills, learn and myinfo

